Recommendation Project:

Knowledge Required: HDFS,MapReduce,Hive,SQL

1)Ingestion

  1)Sqoop Import users,ratings,movies into HDFS(Hadoop Distributed File System).
  2)Create External Hive tables.

2) Association Mining.

   Preprocessing(Ip:Rating,Op:GoodRating)
    1) Remove any movie whose rating < 3.
    2) Remove all movies whose votes < 5

   Recommendations(Ip:GoodRating,Op:MoviesRecommendations)
    1) Find out the similar user
    2) Find out the movies which was watched by similar user which was not watched by base user.

